::Prowl/Zardus/Shredder/DeathStorm::

Prowl returns Iron Raptor's look. "We should get out of here. Three maximals 
against a predacon base arn't good odds."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The doors to Serpentor's quarters zoom open and Zardus walks in. He looks at 
Serpentor.

"You can go back to the predacons if you wish, you know?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Shredder laughs. He turns to Megatron. "Are there CR chambers were we're 
heading?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
DeathStorm walks out into a clearing, almost crashing into a bot. He jumped 
back and looks around the clearing. There were two bots, both maximals. 
(Dinobot and Tavatron)

He narrows his eyes and tenses up, gun ready.
